      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\ude97 A solid, dependable ride that's ready to impress! This vehicle is in good condition \u2014 it runs smoothly, handles great, and has been well cared for over the years. You'll notice only minor cosmetic blemishes consistent with normal use, while the mechanical components are in strong working order. Whether you're commuting daily or hitting the open road, this car delivers a comfortable and confident driving experience. A smart buy for anyone looking for quality without the mint-condition price tag!",
