    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "We're listing this vehicle honestly as a car in mint condition, and we want buyers to have a complete, accurate picture before reaching out. The exterior is truly exceptional \u2014 the paint is deep, glossy, and free of any scratches, chips, or blemishes, with body panels that are perfectly aligned and show no signs of dents or rust. The interior is equally impressive, presenting like new: all upholstery is clean and unmarked, every trim piece is intact, and all electronics, controls, and features function exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, with no leaks, unusual noises, or warning lights \u2014 this vehicle has been meticulously maintained and it shows. Tires have excellent tread remaining, brakes are in great shape, and the suspension feels tight and responsive. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a vehicle that genuinely lives up to the 'mint' label \u2014 no surprises, no hidden issues, just a car that's ready to impress from the moment you see it.",
      "price": 48000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_9_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_9",
      "description": "Here's your chance to own a genuinely mint-condition vehicle that's ready to impress from the moment you lay eyes on it! The exterior is gleaming and virtually blemish-free, with paintwork that still catches the light beautifully. Inside, the cabin is spotless \u2014 fresh, clean, and well-maintained with no signs of heavy wear. Under the hood, everything is in excellent working order, making this a reliable and exciting drive. If you've been searching for a used car that feels as close to new as possible, this is the one to see!",
      "price": 45000.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in mint condition, and the asking price reflects the exceptional quality you'll find \u2014 please read this full description before reaching out. The car is essentially flawless inside and out, presenting like new in every measurable way. The exterior paint retains a deep, uniform shine with no scratches, chips, swirl marks, or blemishes of any kind. All body panels are straight and true, with consistent panel gaps throughout. The interior is immaculate \u2014 the seats, carpeting, headliner, and all trim pieces show zero signs of wear, staining, or deterioration. Every electronic feature, button, and control functions perfectly as intended. Under the hood, the engine bay is clean and well-maintained, and the vehicle runs with smooth, confident power delivery. Mechanically, it is in excellent health: brakes, suspension, steering, and drivetrain all feel tight and responsive. The tires have substantial tread remaining and wear evenly. Service history is up to date, and there are no warning lights, known issues, or deferred maintenance items. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that has been exceptionally well cared for and is truly ready to drive with complete confidence from day one.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in mint condition, and we are genuinely proud to present what is one of the finest examples you will find on the used car market. The exterior is truly exceptional \u2014 the paint is deep, rich, and glossy with absolutely no scratches, chips, or blemishes to speak of. Panel gaps are tight and consistent, all trim pieces are perfectly intact, and the glass is crystal clear without any chips or cracks. Step inside and you'll find an interior that looks and smells virtually new \u2014 the upholstery is spotless, all surfaces are free of wear, and every control, button, and feature functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean, well-maintained, and runs with smooth, confident power. The tires have excellent tread remaining, the brakes are in great shape, and the suspension feels solid and responsive. This is the kind of used car that is genuinely difficult to find \u2014 one where the previous owner clearly took exceptional care of it from day one. If you're looking for a vehicle you can drive with pride and confidence without worrying about near-term maintenance surprises, this one deserves serious consideration.",
      "price": 48500.0,
